snippet.title: CrossPlanet: Free to Play Shooter - Alpha Gameplay
snippet.description:
CrossPlanet is a FREE TO PLAY Third Person Shooter inspired by the curiosity of Halo in third person! We're currently in development for windows PC. Here is 5 minutes of Alpha footage/ gameplay highlights from the developers. 

Join the discord here and talk to devs, test the game, and keep updated weekly: https://discord.gg/wRkCcNEYek
